operator                  precedence
1) !,+,-(unary operator)  --> R to L
2) *,/,%                  --> L to R
3) +,-                    --> L to R
4) <,<=,>,>=              --> L to R
5) ==,!=                  --> L to R
6) &&                     --> L to R
7) ||                     --> L to R
8) =(assignment operator) --> R to L